summary: My name is Atefeh Kamalian. I am an MA graduate in TOEFL at sciences and researches branch of Yazd university. (2011-2013). I had been a teacher in Seyyed Shohada school for a year.I have been teaching in Bou-Ali and Sina language institute about 9 years since 2007. I have been a translator and tutor. I have published some papers and I am going to publish more papers in future.My research interests includes language teaching in general and translation as well as sociolinguistic and discourse analysis
